{"type":"message","id":"b1fa7944","parentId":"af868683","timestamp":"2026-03-29T20:02:31.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the HEARTBEAT.md and related checklist files to understand what needs to be done.\n\nCurrent time: Monday, March 30th, 2026, 4:02 AM (Asia/Shanghai) - this is in the quiet hours (23:00-08:00), so I should be doing internal tasks silently without disturbing the user.\n\nLet me check:\n1. The HEARTBEAT.md content (already in context)\n2. The workspace backup checklist\n3. The quant ops checklist\n4. Self-improvement checklist\n5. ACTIVE_TASK.md if exists\n\nFrom HEARTBEAT.md:\n- Quiet hours: 23:00-08:00, non-urgent keep quiet\n- Scheduled work: workspace backup (daily), quant ops (daily), self-improvement (daily afternoon/evening)\n- Only alert on: precheck failure, strategy audit ALERT, dual-source/heatmap failure, dashboard failure, self-improvement new items\n\nIt's 4:02 AM, well within quiet hours. I should:\n1. Check if there's an ACTIVE_TASK.md to monitor\n\n\n2. Check the checklists\n3. Perform quiet internal tasks\n\nLet me read the relevant files.","thinkingSignature":"9a7dbb26c6e3b9b932f7f95f6ca055402ed12158181984d5e43411f2c65bcc1d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uv24b4bt0ql6_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uv24b4bt0ql6_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uv24b4bt0ql6_3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uv24b4bt0ql6_4","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":66,"output":393,"cacheRe