{"type":"message","id":"68e50320","parentId":"b4d55f81","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:45:00.512Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_73kQfkX55qQ00VqT5edUXbK8|fc_0411becee4eea9850169cbb3ba27048199bb05afe0e38bf216","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md - Periodic Tasks\n\nHeartbeat prompt:\n`Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.`\n\n## Core Rules\n\n- `HEARTBEAT.md` 只保留调度规则；长说明放到 `checklists/`\n- 如果没有新情况，回复 `HEARTBEAT_OK`\n- 晚上 `23:00-08:00` 非紧急情况保持安静；**安静不等于停工**，夜间默认应优先静默执行不需要用户确认的内部任务（如回测、下载、校验、整理、生成报告、同步、备份）\n- 若当天已推送且无新增数据，避免重复打扰\n- 只有三类情况主动汇报：\n  1. 新文件/报告已落地\n  2. 脚本已跑出结果\n  3. 需要用户输入/授权\n\n## Scheduled Work\n\n### 1) Workspace backup\n- 频率：每天一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md`\n\n### 2) Quant ops\n- 盘前强检：交易日 `09:20-09:40`\n- 日常审计 / 增强 / 实盘面板：每天一次 heartbeat 内执行\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md`\n\n### 3) Self-improvement\n- 频率：每天下午或晚间一次\n- Checklist: `checklists/heartbeat-self-improvement.md`\n\n## Quiet / Alert Rules\n\n### 保持安静\n- 非交易日且无异常\n- 当天任务已完成且无新增结果\n- 刚检查过且没有变化\n\n### 主动提醒\n- 盘前强检失败\n- 每日策略审计为 `ALERT`\n- 双源验证/热力图失败\n- 实盘面板生成失败或需要权限\n- self-improvement 有新提升项或新技能草稿\n\n## Memory Maintenance\n\n每隔几天可以在 heartbeat 中做一次：\n- 复盘最近 `memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md`\n- 将稳定结论提升到 `MEMORY.md`\n- 清理过期信息\n\n## Active Task Monitoring\n\n每次 heartbeat 执行时：\n- 检查 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`\n- 若 Status=active 且 Next 有内容：立即用 `sessions_spawn` 以 isolated session 模式触发续跑，或在响应末尾给出 `sessions_yield` 让调度器接手\n- 若 Status=done：清理过期的 ACTIVE_TASK.md（超过 24 小时的 done 任务可归档到 checklists/ACTIVE_TASK_HISTORY/）\n\n**注意**：多步骤任务完成后，必须**在回复末尾显式使用 `sessions_yield`** 或 **发送续跑信号**，而不是结束 turn 等待用户下次触发。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774957500505}}
{"type":"message","id":"98179af5","parentId":"68e50320","timestamp":"2026-03-31T11:45:00.519Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_RwSOnIzCTziWJBWboV9J8DIU|fc_0411becee4eea9850169cbb3ba2b7c81998745b31da5891811","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: active\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-03-31 16:34\nUpdated: 2026-03-31 19:29\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\nUser Trigger: 张玲连续指令“继续”，要求把模拟盘 P0 问题按顺序继续推进，不停在讨论层\nResume Entry: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\n\n## Goal\n- 连续推进模拟盘 P0 修复：完成 T01 宽度 LIVE 预测链修复，并继续完成 T02 执行状态真相源统一、T03 Exit 系降级止血的首轮交付\n\n## Acceptance\n- T01：`ml_predictions_live_latest.csv` 推进到 `2026-03-30`，两套宽度盘 `signal_stale=false`\n- T02：`today_stock_strategy_report`、`strategy_probe_guard_summary`、`control_tower` 都能明确展示统一执行状态字段：`runtime_truth_state` / `can_execute_today` / `buy_authorized` / `blocking_reason`\n- T02：`aggressive` 不再被误报为 `NO_JOURNAL_WITH_PLANNED_ORDERS`，而是正确归因为统一风控阻断\n- T03：`exit_dual / exit_tight` 从“当前有效纸盘”降级为“退出实验/失效盘”，并落地退出失败复盘文件\n- 完成相关 latest 面板刷新，并完成 git 提交\n\n## Current\n- T05：三盘风格重构首轮代码实现，先切 aggressive / balanced / defensive 的盘级 runtime 风险真相\n\n## Next\n- 按盘级 risk truth 重跑 aggressive / balanced / defensive 的 orders、probe_guard、control_tower，验证不再同跌同封\n- 拆分三盘 candidate source / ranking gate / probe budget，形成真正的进取/均衡/防守分层\n- alpha55 单列修复选股/权重输出，解决单日总目标权重长期卡在约 6% 的问题\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-03-31 16:47] 修改 `scripts/train_ml_factors_all_a.py`：拆分回测预测 `test_data` 与 LIVE 推理预测 `live_data`，避免因 `future_return` 缺失裁掉最近特征日期\n- [2026-03-31 17:39] 修复版 LIVE 重训完成；`ml_predictions_live_latest.csv` 最新日期推进到 `2026-03-30`\n- [2026-03-31 17:42] 已重跑 `breadth_aggressive` / `breadth_strict_oos`；两套 latest.json 均已切到 LIVE 预测文件，`signal_date=2026-03-30`、`signal_stale=false`\n- [2026-03-31 17:43] 已刷新 latest 面板与控制塔：breadth dashboards、strategy_performance_panel、control_tower_daily、dashboard_portal\n- [2026-03-31 19:05] 完成 T02 第一轮统一：修改 `run_strategy_probe_guard.py`、`generate_strategy_probe_guard_summary.py`、`generate_today_stock_strategy_report.py`；probe guard 改用 `runtime_risk_state_latest.json` 区分“统一风控阻断”与“应落 journal 未落地”\n- [2026-03-31 19:04] 回归生成 `strategy_probe_guard_summary_latest.json`、`today_stock_strategy_report_latest.json`、`control_tower_daily_latest.json`\n- [2026-03-31 19:04] `paper_aggressive_probe_guard_20260330.json` 已从 `NO_JOURNAL_WITH_PLANNED_ORDERS` 改为 `PLANNED_ORDERS_BLOCKED_BY_RUNTIME_HALT`\n- [2026-03-31 19:12] 完成 T03 第一轮止血：修改 `panel_profile_registry.py`、`generate_strategy_performance_panel.py`、`generate_dashboard_portal.py`，将 `exit_dual / exit_tight` 从“当前有效纸盘”降级为“退出实验/失效盘”\n- [2026-03-31 19:12] 已落地退出失败复盘：`research/reports/paper_exit_failure_postmortem_20260331.md`\n- [2026-03-31 19:12] 已回归刷新 `strategy_performance_panel_latest.*`、`control_tower_daily_latest.*`、`dashboard_portal_latest.html`\n- [2026-03-31 19:15] T02/T03 首轮交付已提交：c8b010400 fix: align runtime truth and downgrade exit profiles\n- T04：低仓位成因诊断，定位 alpha55 / balanced / defensive 高现金占比的真实阻断因子\n- [2026-03-31 19:29] 完成 T04 低仓位诊断：落地 low_exposure_diagnosis_t04_20260331.{json,md}，确认 alpha55 主因是候选不足/权重过小；三盘主因是共享 runtime halt + 预算缩放，不是执行漏单\n- [2026-03-31 19:29] 进入 T05 首轮：落地三盘风格重构蓝图 t05_three_profile_style_refactor_round1_20260331.md\n\n## Evidence\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/train_ml_factors_all_a.py`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/run_logs/t01_ml_train_livefix_20260331.log`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/breadth_aggressive_paper_latest.json`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/breadth_strict_oos_paper_latest.json`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_strategy_probe_guard.py`\n- `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_strategy_probe_guard_summary.py`\n-